,"descendants":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"2685632513","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685632513","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTYzMjUxMw==","status":"current","title":"Tpago","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":10589376},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685632513","tinyui":"/x/AYATo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685632513","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685632513/Tpago","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685632513"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"92d5faf7-8b78-46c1-8aea-d4bf48b68682\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para la funcionalidad de actualizar tarjetas vencidas(de forma as&iacute;ncrona) durante el proceso de cobro de suscripciones, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"5f0f0f5470b8a90025b61555\" ri:local-id=\"39351a81-2342-443b-95f4-691e64bf7e5c\" /></ac:link> .</p><p>Las horas estimadas son: <strong> 62 ~ 10  d&iacute;as</strong></p><p>Fecha de Inicio: <time datetime=\"2025-09-26\" /> </p><p>Fecha estimada de Entrega: <time datetime=\"2025-10-10\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p /><table data-table-width=\"818\" data-layout=\"center\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 332.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 148.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 337.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Servicio / Portal</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Crear l&oacute;gica y servicio para llamar al servicio RPG.</p><ul><li><p>Nuevo archivo YML</p></li><li><p>Nueva capa de service</p></li><li><p>Nueva capa de l&oacute;gica</p></li></ul></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">10</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Crear una nueva tabla para auditor&iacute;a de actualizaci&oacute;n de tarjetas.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">3</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Crear proceso as&iacute;ncrono que llame al servicio RPG, actualize la tarjeta y re-intente el pago.</p><ul><li><p>Crear registros de log en la tabla cuando se actualiza la tarjeta.</p></li><li><p>Loggear el proceso en un logger nuevo</p></li></ul></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">20</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Modificar l&oacute;gica de obtener configuraciones para aceptar listas y separar por comas los valores.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Verificar si el pago fall&oacute; por tarjeta vencida, clave cambiada o tarjeta perdida. Encolar la tarea en caso afirmativo.</p><ul><li><p>Solo aplica para tarjetas de cr&eacute;dito de Paraguay.</p></li><li><p>Crear configuraci&oacute;n en la base de datos de tipo array que contega los tipos de errores</p></li></ul></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Salida a Staging</p><ul><li><p>Integraci&oacute;n de los flujos</p></li><li><p>Tests</p></li><li><p>Creaci&oacute;n y correci&oacute;n de PRs</p></li><li><p>Pruebas locales</p></li><li><p>Armado de ramas</p></li><li><p>Deploy a STG</p></li><li><p>Pruebas iniciales en STG</p></li></ul></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">10</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">55</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">7</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">62</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr></tbody></table><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4230610945"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":91994866},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4230610945/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4230610945/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4230610945/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4230610945/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4230610945","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4230610945/Actualizaci+n+de+tarjetas+vencidas+en+el+proceso+de+cobro+de+suscripciones+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4230610945","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4230610945","tinyui":"/x/AQAq-/","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}